des:
I cannot wait to introduce you to my friend Fanny. Fanny is a rather unique girl, then again, lots of things can seem a bit strange until you take the time to understand them. 

Figure Out Fanny is a fun word puzzle requiring observation and deduction. Through a series of challenges you’ll get to know Fanny, and if you are clever you will uncover the secret to understanding this peculiar young lady. Will you be able to make sense of Fanny? Let’s find out!
